    "Html": "For the CellStyle you can do this:<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">\r\n<p>Style </p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px\">style = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">Style</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">typeof</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">DataGridCell</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">));<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">EventSetter</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> eventSetter = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">EventSetter<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">{<br>\r\n    Event = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">DataGridCell</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">.PreviewMouseLeftButtonDownEvent,<br>\r\n    Handler = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">MouseButtonEventHandler</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">(DataGridCell_PreviewMouseLeftButtonDown)<br>\r\n};<br>\r\nstyle.Setters.Add(eventSetter);<br>\r\nDataGrid_Standard.CellStyle = style;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n",
